      "message": "A focused test for `fetch.autogc\u003dfalse` would be great, but I noticed the original auto-gc change I68a2a051 also did not add tests for the existing `receive.autogc` behavior.\n\nSo I wouldn’t necessarily block this change on tests alone. It may be reasonable to handle broader auto-gc config coverage in a follow-up, covering both `receive.autogc` and `fetch.autogc`.",
